DESCRIPTION:Required case reading before class starts in June.\nCase: Apex Ski Boots (520013-PDF-ENG)\nAccess via Canvas: https://canvas.mit.edu/courses/38464\n\nGroup Report Due: June 12 at start of class.\n\nDiscussion Questions:\n1. Why are consumers not recognizing the value of this product?\n2. Why is Apex having trouble selling through specialty stores?\n3. If successful, are there entry barriers to prevent competitors?\n4. Would a major brand be more likely to succeed with a similar product?\n5. Bargaining power analysis between Apex and dominant retailer.
