BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:15809-pre-reading-ipl@mit.edu
SUMMARY:📚 READ: Indian Premier League (SPM38-PDF-ENG) — REQUIRED BEFORE CLASS
DESCRIPTION:Required case reading before class starts in June.\nCase: Indian Premier League (SPM38-PDF-ENG)\nAccess via Canvas: https://canvas.mit.edu/courses/38464\n\nGroup Report Due: July 10 at start of class.\n\nDiscussion Questions:\n1. Why was the league successful in its first season and how sustainable is this?\n2. What advantages does having franchisees managing teams provide?\n3. How do the league's goals potentially differ from team owners?\n4. What mechanisms did the league use to align objectives?\n5. Advantages and disadvantages of delaying franchise sales until after first season?
